name: Van Gogh's Starry Night by Zaam
description: The Starry Night is an oil on canvas painting by Dutch Post-Impressionist painter Vincent van Gogh. Painted in June 1889, it depicts the view from the east-facing window of his asylum room just before sunrise, with the addition of an imaginary village.  This is my version of the starry night in the modern world, Created through manipulation and collaboration with an A.I
